---
import TerminalWindow from './TerminalWindow.astro';
---

<section class="py-20 px-4 sm:px-6 border-t border-border">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-center mb-4">
      How it works
    </h2>
    <p class="text-text-muted text-center max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-16">
      Add machines to your fleet. Your agents show up automatically. No cloud, no YAML, no infrastructure.
    </p>

    <!-- Steps -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent/20 text-accent font-mono font-bold text-sm mb-4">1</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Install on each machine</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">
          <code class="text-xs bg-bg-card px-1.5 py-0.5 rounded border border-border">pip install marmy</code> on every machine in your fleet. A lightweight daemon connects your agents to the app.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent/20 text-accent font-mono font-bold text-sm mb-4">2</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Pair and add machines</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">
          Scan the QR code or enter the pairing key. Each machine joins your fleet — over LAN or Tailscale. Direct connection, no cloud relay.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="inline-flex items-center justify-center w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-accent/20 text-accent font-mono font-bold text-sm mb-4">3</div>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2">Structure your team</h3>
        <p class="text-text-muted text-sm">
          Define agent roles, assign leads and sub-agents, set up autonomous schedules. Marmy turns a pile of sessions into a coordinated operation.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Architecture diagram -->
    <TerminalWindow title="architecture" class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <pre class="text-xs sm:text-sm"><span class="text-text-muted">┌──────────────┐</span>         <span class="text-text-muted">┌───────────────────┐</span>         <span class="text-text-muted">┌──────────────┐</span>
<span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  <span class="text-accent">Your Phone</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">ws://</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  <span class="text-green">marmy agent</span>      <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">stdin/</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  <span class="text-text-primary">Claude Code</span> <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>
<span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  React Native <span class="text-text-muted">│ ◄──────► │</span>  Python daemon    <span class="text-text-muted">│ ◄──────► │</span>  (subprocess) <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>
<span class="text-text-muted">│</span>              <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>         <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>                   <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">stdout</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>              <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>
<span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">Fleet view</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>         <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">One per machine</span>   <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>         <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">N sessions</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>
<span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">Team mgmt</span>   <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>         <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">WebSocket on</span>     <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>         <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">per machine</span> <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>
<span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">Scheduling</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>         <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>  <span class="text-text-muted">:8765 (LAN/TS)</span>   <span class="text-text-muted">│</span>         <span class="text-text-muted">└──────────────┘</span>
<span class="text-text-muted">└──────────────┘</span>         <span class="text-text-muted">└───────────────────┘</span></pre>
    </TerminalWindow>
  </div>
</section>
